{"tid":2432024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無證據顯示，上水廢老清潔工死於掟磚","createTime":"2021-03-04T04:42:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T04:58:18.000Z","uid":42188,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cd85c552d71a14f78a3b905d5f9c1c851b4535fe","tid":2432024,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:42:21.000Z","msg":"事發於去年11月13日，上水龍運街北區大會堂外馬路有一批黑衣人聚集堵路，期間疑因政見問題，與另一批男女互相指罵，繼而有人掟磚頭及擸竹枝互毆。混亂間，食環署一名70歲外判清潔工羅長清疑被磚頭掟中，登時倒地失去知覺，有人將他抬離現場。羅送院後出現腦幹死亡迹象，<span class=\"red\">延至翌晚10時51分證實不治</span>。案件列作謀殺案，交由新界北警區重案組跟進。<br />\n<br />\n打完針2日之後死都話唔關科興事<br />\n咁呢單點解有關？都唔係即時死亡<br />\n個70歲廢老本身都有長期病患，例如高血壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db6abadf6d38899bd8bb19bda657049386f0b4d0","tid":2432024,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hEc9sVH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhEc9sVH.png&h=dda01b3f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8zDMu82.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8zDMu82.png&h=5cdf5c97&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}